cs.NI, cs.SY, cs.IT, cs.DC, cs.PL 

This paper deals with the analysis of networks, which is a topic that falls under the category of computer networks (cs.NI). The paper also discusses safety-critical systems, which is a subfield of systems and control (cs.SY). The use of optimization techniques and algorithms is a key aspect of the paper, which suggests that it could also be classified under information theory (cs.IT) and distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC). Finally, the paper proposes a new algorithm for deterministic network calculus, which is a subfield of programming languages (cs.PL).
